QuestData.Title: Disruption of Power
QuestData.Description:
The naga are tapping into some latent power, infusing the energy into some manner of device.
I do not know what purpose they have for this power, but it is surely in our interest to destroy the objects before they can be used against us.
QuestData.LogDescription: Destroy $1oa Ley Line Accumulators in Spears of Azshara.
